    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="820158118">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-820158118" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-820158118" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="820158118">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/princeps/">princeps</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-06-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">现在做《老子》却没读过《史官特色》，大概就像读《四书》不读朱子章句一样了吧。书的水准还不如刘笑敢那本台版的《老子》。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="324399664">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-324399664" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-324399664" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="324399664">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/conscience/">种瓜得瓜</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-12-15</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">《论语》其实大多是理想，中国人所谓的那点生存“智慧”，源头在《老子》。把经典说的大家都明白，而又不趋附人心，李零先生此书值得一读，说老子者也众，若时间不够，读此书亦尽可以做大致了解了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="962874986">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-962874986" class="vote-count">0</span>
